---
// src/components/sections/LearningSystemInfographic.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        How we build your learning system
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMuted">
        A professional eLearning project needs more than pages. It needs structure, delivery, learner experience, and a practical launch process.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline Wrapper -->
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Connecting Line (Desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-brand-border -translate-y-1/2 z-0 rounded"></div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 relative z-10">

        {/* Step 1 */}
        <div class="reveal-card flex flex-col items-center text-center relative" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
          <!-- Mobile Line Connector -->
          <div class="md:hidden absolute top-12 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-brand-border -translate-x-1/2 -z-10"></div>

          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white border-4 border-brand-softBlue flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-primary text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 absolute top-0 -mt-2">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Understand</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We review your audience, content, platform, and launch goals.</p>
        </div>

        {/* Step 2 */}
        <div class="reveal-card flex flex-col items-center text-center relative" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
           <div class="md:hidden absolute top-12 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-brand-border -translate-x-1/2 -z-10"></div>

          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white border-4 border-brand-softBlue flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9h18"/><path d="M9 21V9"/><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" ry="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-primary text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 absolute top-0 -mt-2">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Structure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We organize the learning journey, modules, pages, offers, and CTAs.</p>
        </div>

        {/* Step 3 */}
        <div class="reveal-card flex flex-col items-center text-center relative" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
           <div class="md:hidden absolute top-12 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-brand-border -translate-x-1/2 -z-10"></div>

          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white border-4 border-brand-softBlue flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m18 16 4-4-4-4"/><path d="m6 8-4 4 4 4"/><path d="m14.5 4-5 16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-primary text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 absolute top-0 -mt-2">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Build</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We create the course, pages, LMS setup, and visual learning experience.</p>
        </div>

        {/* Step 4 */}
        <div class="reveal-card flex flex-col items-center text-center relative" style="animation-delay: 400ms;">
           <div class="md:hidden absolute top-12 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-brand-border -translate-x-1/2 -z-10"></div>

          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white border-4 border-brand-softBlue flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-primary text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 absolute top-0 -mt-2">4</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Automate</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We connect forms, emails, offers, checkout, and student access where needed.</p>
        </div>

        {/* Step 5 */}
        <div class="reveal-card flex flex-col items-center text-center relative" style="animation-delay: 500ms;">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand-accent text-white border-4 border-brand-softGreen flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-md hover-lift">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"/><path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"/><path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"/><path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-accent text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 absolute top-0 -mt-2">5</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Launch</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain">We test, refine, train your team, and prepare for real users.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
